org.netbeans.modules.bugtracking.spi

Class IssuePriorityInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.modules.bugtracking.spi.IssuePriorityInfo

  • public final class IssuePriorityInfo
extends Object
    Represents information related to one particular issue priority. The Priority attributes are used in various Task Dashboard features - e.g. Icon is shown next to an Issue, etc.
    Since:
    1.85
